Meslo LGS Nerd Font
===================

Files in this directory (MesloLGS NF *.ttf) are the Meslo LG S typeface
patched with the Nerd Fonts glyph set. They are bundled with dotctl for
convenience and are NOT covered by dotctl's GPLv3 license - they retain
their original upstream licenses as described below.

